CM NEC Input File Bi-Quad for 2440 MHz, Trevor Marshall, 9/1/2001
CM All data in wavelengths,will scale to 300MHz
CM Square copper reflector,w/w choke,modelled as 0.05 lamda mesh
CM Things Fixed:
CM 1. Several lines were missing the last fields. Some apps can handle this but not xnec2c
CM 2. The GW wire cards mostly had segments tags of zero, all wires must have different nonzero tags
CM 3. The RP tag specified gain averaging, which is not supported for xnec2c
CM 4. After adding and changing the wire tags, the excitation was applied to the wrong segment, fixed that
CM 5. xnec2c doesn't plot the frequency data if you only five a single frequency, so I set a range of 300 to 400 MHz
